</span>e.<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp; </span></span><span>Assume
the same 50-hour week and that the employer has definitely established a we=
ekly
pay period and has a monthly settlement period. The salesperson draws $150 a
week against earned commissions. This salesperson has not been paid in
