</span>b.<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp; </span></span><span>On
the other hand, where the employer does prescribe a specific type and style=
 of
clothing to be worn at work, e.g. where a restaurant or hotel requires a tu=
xedo
or a skirt and blouse or jacket of a specific or distinctive style, color, =
or
quality, such clothing would be considered uniforms.</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph><span>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-left:1.5in;text-indent:-1.5in'>=
