le
hours worked in the week (i.e., average hourly earnings for the workweek af=
ter
the deductions are not less than the highest applicable MW enforced by
WH).&nbsp; (See Regs 531.35 and 531.36.) Deductions for non-3(m) items that=
 cut
into the highest applicable MW enforced by WH are illegal in a non-OT workw=
eek
unless the law establishing that MW (e.g., DBRA, SCA, H-2A, H-1B, etc.) all=
ows
